383
00:29:36.340 --> 00:29:40.320
Something that the films director, out gay
filmmaker Bill Condon, played up in the press

384
00:29:40.320 --> 00:29:45.440
for literally months beforehand. Creating
much controversy from parents groups and much

385
00:29:45.440 --> 00:29:50.510
anticipation from gay fans. After all, Beauty
and the Beast was Howard Ashmen’s swan song

386
00:29:50.510 --> 00:29:55.290
before his untimely death from complications
due to AIDS, so it would be a fitting tribute

387
00:29:55.290 --> 00:30:00.130
to him to finally put a real gay character
in a Disney movie. And then the scene happened

388
00:30:00.130 --> 00:30:03.410
and the audience said… that was it?

389
00:30:03.410 --> 00:30:09.250
Yes, that was it. Like Star Wars The Rise
