429
00:33:24.491 --> 00:33:25.491
to go out on. 

430
00:33:25.491 --> 00:33:29.890
Now, as a movie news nerd I followed the production
of Birds of Prey pretty closely. So I knew

431
00:33:29.890 --> 00:33:34.570
that WB actually sent this thing back for
reshoots at least once because they decided,

432
00:33:34.570 --> 00:33:39.290
late in the game, that a certain plot point
was a bit too risque for them. You see, originally,

433
00:33:39.290 --> 00:33:43.940
Ewan McGregor’s Black Mask was 100% confirmed
to be gay in the movie, and the reason he

434
00:33:43.940 --> 00:33:48.370
was after the Bertinelli diamond wasn’t
